{{Infobox journal | title = Archiv für Rechts- und Sozialphilosophie | cover = | editor = Annette Brockmöller | discipline = [[Philosophy]] | language = English, French, German, Spanish | abbreviation = Arch. Rechts Sozialphilos. | publisher = [[Franz Steiner Verlag]] | country = | frequency = Quarterly | history = 1907–present | openaccess = | impact = | impact-year = | website = http://www.steiner-verlag.de/ARSP | link1 = http://www.steiner-verlag.de/ARSP/ARSP3.html | link1-name = Online tables of contents | link2 = | link2-name = | JSTOR = | OCLC = 699621635 | LCCN = 10004160 | CODEN = | ISSN = 0001-2343 | eISSN = }} '''''Archiv für Rechts- und Sozialphilosophie''''' (English: ''Archives for Philosophy of Law and Social Philosophy'') is a quarterly [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] of [[philosophy]]. It was established in 1907 and is the official journal of the [[Internationale Vereinigung für Rechts- und Sozialphilosophie]]. The journal is abstracted and indexed in the [[Index to Foreign Legal Periodicals]], [[Index Philosophicus]], [[Francis (database)|Francis]], [[Russian Academy of Sciences Bibliographies]], [[The Philosopher's Index]], [[Répertoire Bibliographique de la Philosophie]], [[International Bibliography of the Social Sciences]], and [[PhilPapers]].
